Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's start something fun.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We were told by them to do a manzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- So we do a half hour manzai.\N- That sounds like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.21,0:00:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Manzai is usually  about 15 minutes, right?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do it for 30 minutes.\NSounds fun, doesn't it?\NYou're also excited, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I'm done, I'm going to line up the staff and beat them up one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine, but this time we're going to be able to do our manzai to the hilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, that's good.\N- It doesn't seem like you want to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.63,0:00:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't get to do manzai in Tokyo very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- So today we'll see how it goes.\N- I wonder what will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, they are looking for students.\N- Let's join.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Downtown no\NGaki no tsukai ya arahende!!\N#0001
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for walking in so sloppily, even though we' re young.\NBut it's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even young people have tough times.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- I can't move the way I want. I know it's the first shot, so I'll do my best, but my joints hurt.\N- What the hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's been a long time since I've done a manzai.\NI miss it.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.23,0:01:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- People in Tokyo don't know us.\N- Of course they don't, because we haven't been to any shows in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Many people don't know which agency we belong to.\NWe belong to Yoshimoto Kogyo.\N- Do you know Yoshimoto Kogyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's well-known among the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- It’s known for its low remuneration and for making us work like slaves.\N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do this calmly in these places, but it's difficult to do it at Namba Grand kagetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Because the bigwigs from Yoshimoto come to see us.\N- They come to see us while we are doing manzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The bigwigs from the head office come to the back of the seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- If I say "the bigwigs from Yoshimoto," it's too long, so I say "yakuza".\N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not yakuza.\NThey look like them, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sometimes the chairman comes to see the show.\N- Do you know the chairman of Yoshimoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He is an old coot named Shonosuke Hayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He has gray hair and a cane.\NHe doesn't need it because he is in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- He has a cane because he wants to poke comedians with it.\N- Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- "I want to poke them," he often says.\N- Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes guys like that come to see us.\NSo it's difficult to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- He looks at us on stage with a furrowed brow.\N- He never laughs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NHe sees us with this looks on his face.\NHe doesn't know much about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Even though we are Yoshimoto.\N- He doesn't know us because there are so many comedians.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- He called someone.\N- While we are doing our manzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who is that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who is that on stage right now?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"They're Downtown."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- "Delete them."\N- Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how bad he is, he won't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- He says a lot of irresponsible things.\N- He doesn't even think of us as humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He says a lot of irresponsible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day I met some bigwigs and I said, "Thank you for everything".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- He said to me, "I still don't know what you said".\N- That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I'm not very smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I can't understand what I'm saying.\NI know that, but I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when I'm speaking now, you can't see my upper teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My upper lip is long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's a disease.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying my best to speak forward, but my voice hits back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He tries to speak, but his voice hits here and it doesn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- I explained it to him.\NThen he said, "Cut around the mouth."\N- Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cut there, I'll see your gums and it'll be disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:04:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had to do that, so I talked to mom about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom also agonized over it for about three days and said, "If you want to do it, then do it".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- So I went to the hospital and they drew just a cut line here.\N- Where is it drawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I became a comedian to make money.\NBut I can't make much money at Yoshimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- I think we are going the wrong way.\N- Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There were several professions I wanted to be when I was a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people want to be athletes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pilots, doctors...\NI wanted to be a school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked the teachers in TV dramas who worked hard with their students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There are usually pros and cons.\NThere are good teachers and bad teachers.\NA teacher with a bad personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My gym teacher in high school was like that.\NI hated him.\NHe would not admit his mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- He never tried to fix them?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:05:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Everyone, today you will have a bar test.\NFirst, I'll show you how to do it.\NDo it just like I did."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We watched him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,While rolling on the bar,  the teacher fell to the ground and cracked his head open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,His brain came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Are you okay!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher stood up and said.\N"Do this."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way he would say that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Everyone's brain was out by the fifth period.\N- Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to say that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How can there be a teacher like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to be a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to be a doctor, but they have to think about their patients.\NSuppose your child gets sick and you take him to a doctor.\NIt's hard for the parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"Doctor, how is my son?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Masao going to be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you Masao-kun's father?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, you and he have similar eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,His mouth looks like your wife's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He does that move a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I took his X-rays the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There are about eight of them, so I put them up in the hallway.\NLet me know if there is a photo number you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know if there's one I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Masao-kun taken from a meteorological satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- You took this picture of him from a distance.\N- Yes, I have a good shot of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be difficult to understand without explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the knowledge, so please tell me simply.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. Let me put it simply.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a problem with his lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,His lungs are like "baaaang".\NAnd his gut is like "baaang".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wish it could have been like "bang" here, but it's more like "bang" here than I thought it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I was talking with everyone earlier about how I wish here was like "bang".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you.\N- How am I supposed to understand that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone can explain it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is "baang", you bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Please be serious!\N- I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It‘s really serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Masao-kun has cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, please be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I was taken by surprise by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Masao-kun has cancer.\NThere are various kinds of cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,His cancer is malignant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In medical terms, it's a "really bad cancer".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot guarantee his life.\NHe has six months to live and he will die as early as the second Saturday at 2:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, can't you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing I can do either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:08:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You must never tell him that he has cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that the only way?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Masao, wait over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having an important talk with him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, please say something to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Masao-kun, don't listen to this conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you wait outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a cancer patient, don't move so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to die anyway!\NIf you move so much, your cancer will get even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You are hateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't let him find out about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who told me not to let him find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiz shows these days are fun, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't change the subject!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me not to mention this, and I told him to go over there.\NWhat do you mean, "quiz shows are fun"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiz shows these days are fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it's fun, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you fucking kidding me?\N- There are so many quiz shows these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In one show, if you answer 10 questions correctly, you get a prize of one million yen and a travel to Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make more money by participating in quiz shows than by working.\NBut it's hard to get the right answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's do a quiz today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you the questions and you answer them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you answer the quiz correctly, you get one million yen in prize money.\NPlus a travel to Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that much in return, but I would like something in return.\NPlease consider my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- If you get the answer right, I'll switch from tomorrow between being the "boke" and the "tsukkomi" with you.\N- I don't want to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want a million yen or a travel to Hawaii, but I do want a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Philippines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I get it right, I can go on a travel to the Philippines?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but tomorrow you'll be a Filipino.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't want to be!\N- You'll move your residency to the Philippines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, think of a reward.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,First question.\N{\i1} Taro-kun went to the flower shop to buy flowers.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, what do you think?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tick-tock, tick-tock.\N- Don't say tick-tock!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that question?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"He went to the flower shop to buy flowers.\NSo, what do you think? Tick-tock, tick-tock."\NAre you fucking kidding me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stomping Quiz!!\N- Listen to me!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Time for a stomping quiz.\N- What in hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the answer to that crazy question?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say tick-tock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's a stomping quiz all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- It’s stomping quiz.\N- So what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully and answer.\NThis is the second question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hanako-san went to a public bath.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, what do you think?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say tick-tock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And what am I supposed to answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hanako-san went to a public bath.\NSo, what do you think?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And what am I supposed to answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She got refreshed, didn't she!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me an answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think that's so-so, then tell me the right answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the quiz confusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the point!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer to settle things through discussion as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to say to a question like this?\NYou answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I will make the question easier to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that obvious!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why didn't you do it from the start?\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san, I've never done anything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's you who answers, I'll make the question easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but you'll have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taro-kun went to the public bath.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taro-kun loves to take a bath.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He sometimes goes there twice a day in summer.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, what do you think?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as before!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter to me if he goes there two or three times a summer, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a clear-cut question instead of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to get punched in the face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Exotic Quiz!!\N- What the hell is that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- It’s exotic quiz.\N- It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If Taro went to the public bath, what would be the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- It’s exotic quiz.\N- It doesn't matter. What the hell is....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ding-dong\NDing-dong\NDing-dong\NDing-dong
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- The buzzer went off.\N- I don't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a bonus quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can answer this, it will be doubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- It will be doubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What will be doubled?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually,  your points are doubled.\NBut you haven't answered a single question correctly yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way I can answer a question like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I will be doubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be doubled?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda want to see that, I'll try to answer correctly
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- If I double, I will never disrespect you.\N- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san, you are picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, wait.\N- You complains a lot. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone will say the same thing to you that I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can pick your category.\NShowbiz, history, sociology and geography.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You have already made the right answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Which one will you pick?\N- If you had done that from the beginning, I wouldn't have yelled at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sorry.\N- Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- What can I pick from?\N- Showbiz, history, sociology and geography.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Geography.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Geography?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:13:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Geography...okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You should not pick that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't I just pick one I like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How about history?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't I just pick one I like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one would you pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Showbiz.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Showbiz....?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Geography?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier you said I shouldn't pick Geography.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then history.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,History?\NYou want a history quiz?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- You want a history quiz?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- I said earlier that I would be doubled, and now I'm going to be multiplied by 4.\N- What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be quadrupled!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll try to answer correctly\N- History question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taisuke Itagaki.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, what do you think?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Give the same quiz to the audience.\NAnd give me your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to give the next quiz, just tell me the answer to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You only give a question, but you don't give an answer.\NWhat am I supposed to say to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Give your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Last Chance Quiz!!\N- Listen to me!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's time for the Last Chance Quiz.\N- Answer it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is the last chance.\N- Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is your last chance, good luck!\N- Better yet, give me the answer to the question you just asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the answer to your earlier question!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this question confusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the point!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering 1 mark as 46 yen would be comprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell does that make it comprehensible!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you answer this correctly, Hamada-san will become a Filipino.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last chance.\NYou bet on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You are messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:15:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last chance quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Make it an easy question.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to the question carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Were there 60 apples in the colander?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ding-dong, ding-dong!\NCorrect! You are a Filipino!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Quiz: You are a Filipino from tomorrow."\NSee you next week at this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the first time I've ever been tired after doing a manzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I spoke faster than I thought I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you a littl e nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe so. So let's not do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we're going to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,don't stop.\NWe didn't have enough time today, we have to do it again next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- But...\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't have enough time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then next week, let's do it for 40 minutes, doubling the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How about changing the clientele?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's clientele was mostly female office workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So next week, let's invite Indians.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if they are silent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- We have a great curry joke.\N- We don't have such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Curry joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's think about that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to change the clientele?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought today was the best one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do 30 or 40 minutes on time next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff probably thinks, "What the heck are these guys doing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't nod, Yanaoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's do a spirited manzai next week after a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not this week?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you do it from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is a 2:10 AM broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You have a problem with the air time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The guys watching this are probably sleepwalking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make people laugh in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's probably no other comedy show going on tv right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No other TV station does comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Nihon TV does this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a comedy show at 2:10 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes it a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Broadcast the current part.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the first one was still not good enough for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, can you do a half hour next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else but you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...hmm....yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something like, " Of course I can".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we' ll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"Maybe"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be airing Downtown's manzai again next week.\NIn the meantime, please watch plenty of our manzai next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Subbed by RAIDEN1017]
